    {
      "id": "beta-onboarding-path-note-artifact-principles",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Handshake Artifact Principles",
      "position": {
        "x": -80,
        "y": 520
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 280,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Handshake Artifact Principles\n\nThe handshake graph should:\n- acknowledge receipt of the onboarding instructions\n- indicate that the model understands its role\n- encourage the user to talk to the model briefly\n- then encourage asking for another graph\n\nIt should be a proof artifact, not a final destination.",
