        "markdown": "# Handshake Artifact Principles\n\n- The first graph is created by the LLM.\n- It acknowledges receipt of the onboarding instructions.\n- It indicates understanding of the assistant role.\n- It should encourage the user to talk with the LLM for a while, then ask for another graph.\n- The exact copy can vary; the role of the artifact should not.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
