      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Bootstrap View Strategy\n\n- `idle` view: explain what happens and expose the copy action\n- `copied` view: confirm success and show the next step clearly\n- `waiting` view: emphasize paste/import\n- `imported` view: celebrate the handoff briefly, then direct attention into the returned graph\n\nThe bootstrap node should demonstrate visible stateful behavior, not just relay instructions.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
